TextEng: I am acting as a guard. I need information.
Text: 지금 경비 임무 중인데, 정보가 필요합니다.

TextEng: Me like a guard. Me gots questions.
Goodbye.
Any places here that is interesting?
How widespread is the plague here?
I need infomation about the Docks district.
Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 일이나 소문을 들은 게 있나요?

TextEng: How big is plague spread here?
Me wants information about Docks.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료제를 찾으려는 시도에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
Any locations of interest in this district?
Text: 이 지구에 관심 둘만한 장소가 있을까요?

TextEng: A place to get supplies.
Important places. Anything like that?
Who are the important people in this district?
Text: 이 지구의 영향력 있는 인물이라면 누가 있을까요?

TextEng: Who run this place? You know about them?
Text: 여긴 누가 굴리나? 그 사람들 알아?

TextEng: A tavern or inn.
I just need to ask a few questions.
Me just wants ask few questions.
Don't tell me where to go. I do what I want.
Text: 어디 가라 마라 하지 마. 난 내 맘대로 해.

TextEng: You shut up. Me goes whatever me want!
Text: 입 다물어. 나 가고 싶은 데 간다!

TextEng: I will leave.
Me leave.
Back to my other questions about locations.
Back to other stuff in the area.
Who are the Bloodsailors?
Bloodsailors? Who that?
So they are pirates?
So they just pirates?
Who is their leader now?
Who lead them now?
Where would he hide?
Where me find him?
His men can't like that kind of attention.
Text: 그의 부하들은 그런 관심을 좋아하지 않겠군.

TextEng: Pirates not like attention like that.
Vengaul is putting on a show?
Vengaul put on show? What you mean? Juggling?
Text: 벵골이 쇼 한다고? 무슨 말? 저글링?

TextEng: Are there a lot of other guards? Could they get here if I attacked you?
Text: 다른 경비병들이 많아? 내가 널 공격하면 그들이 올 수 있어?

TextEng: Is there lots of other guards in heres? Could they gets here if me attacked you?
Text: 여기 다른 경비병 많아? 나 너 공격하면 그들 올 수 있어?

TextEng: So you'd realize you are at my mercy! Give me all your gold!
Text: 네가 내 자비에 달렸다는 걸 알게 하려고! 금 전부 내놔!

TextEng: Just so's you can't gets help! Give me all yous gold!
Text: 너 도움 못 받는다는 거 알게! 금 다 내놔!

TextEng: No reason. Back to my other questions.
Text: 별 이유 없어. 다른 질문으로 돌아갈게.

TextEng: Eh, no reasons. Back to other questions, okay?
Text: 아, 이유 없어. 다른 질문으로 돌아갈게, 알았지?

TextEng: Nevermind. Farewell for now.
Nothing. Bye for nows.
